The perfectly balanced blend of alcohol, tea and fresh lemon flavor create a refreshing, smooth beverage that’s just a little twisted.

Data.Name: Twisted Tea Hard Iced Tea Original
Data.Description: You'll love Twisted Tea Original’s true iced tea taste. For a refreshing and smooth taste, Twisted Tea uses select tea and natural lemon flavor. It’s delicious. It’s a little twisted.

Data.Name: Kris Pinot Grigio
Data.Description: Ironically, “grigio” means “gray” in Italian, which couldn’t be further from the truth in the case of Kris, which is bursting with colorful aromas and flavors developed in high vineyards of the Veneto region. With enticing aromas of acacia flowers, lime, tangerine and hints of apricots and almonds, KRIS Pinot Grigio is bold but clean and refreshing on the palate, and offers a long finish tinged with orange blossom and honey.

Data.Name: Ketel One Citroen
Data.Description:
Citroen has a wonderful hint of citrus in the flavor with the same smooth taste as regular Ketel One.
 
Prized for its smooth taste, Ketel One starts with the finest wheat and water. As the distillate is heated over a gentle, hand-stoked fire, the temperature and alcohol levels are regulated to ensure the best possible vodka. Not surprisingly, Ketel One has a developed a passionate following among vodka connoisseurs.

Data.Name: Twisted Tea Raspberry Cans
Data.Description:
Raspberries are a symbol of kindness. Impress your afternoon party pals with that fact, while serving them this great-tasting hard iced tea. And don't be surprised if they say “would you kindly get me another one?”
ABV: 5%

Data.Name: Truly Colima Lime
Data.Description: Truly Hard Seltzer is light, crisp and refreshing with a hint of fruit flavor. 5% alc./vol., 100 calories, 1 gram of sugar, gluten free.

Data.Name: Troegs Independent Brewing Perpetual IPA
Data.Description:
At Tröegs, artisanal meets mechanical in a state of IPA we call Perpetual. Cycling through our HopBack vessel and dry-hopping method, this bold Imperial Pale Ale emerges rife with sticky citrus rind, pine balm and tropical fruit.

What we can taste from the beer: pine balm, bold hops, citrus rind

Data.Name: Switchback Ale
Data.Description: Switchback Ale was developed as a flavor concept, not adhering to any style guidelines. Using only traditional ingredients, Switchback Ale is an unfiltered, reddish-amber ale which is particularly well-balanced, allowing for complexity of flavor coupled with an unusually smooth and refreshing character. Five different malts, select hop varieties, and our own specially cultivated yeast create an ale which leads with hop flavors and a subtle impression of fruit (our yeast’s contribution), followed by a palate pleasing malty finish.

Data.Name: Stella Artois Cans
Data.Description: Stella Artois is a classic Belgian lager, golden in color with exceptional clarity and a spicy hop character. Stella Artois' crisp, refreshing flavor pairs well with intensely flavored Thai, Asian fusion and Indian dishes such as curries. The bitterness also helps cut through cream sauces in pastas and contrasts the creaminess of flavorful semi-soft cheeses such as havarti, morbier and artisanal cheddars.

Data.Name: Smithwick's Irish Ale
Data.Description: Smithwick's (pronounced 'smith-icks') is an Irish red ale style beer from Kilkenny in Ireland. Smithwicks was originally brewed in St. Francis Abbey Brewery in Kilkenny, known as 'Smithwicks Brewery' until c.2000. The brewery is situated on the site of a Franciscan abbey where monks had brewed ale since the 14th century, and has ruins of the original abbey on its grounds. It is Irelands oldest operating brewery, founded by John Smithwick in 1710 on land owned by the Duke of Ormonde.[2] It is the major ale producer in Ireland. It was purchased from Irish Ale Breweries in 1965 by Guinness and is now, along with Guinness, part of Diageo. Smithwicks for the domestic market is brewed in Kilkenny and the higher strength export variety is brewed in Dundalk.

Data.Name: Smirnoff Ice Raspberry Burst
Data.Description:
Classic Smirnoff Ice in a delicious and crisp raspberry flavor. Get one to enjoy, serve chilled, or surprise your friends by "icing" them. 

Smirnoff Ice-ing Someone:
"A malted beverage (hence not a vodka like other Smirnoff products) that one is forced to drink when presented, usually in some ceremonious fashion at a large gathering, in an act called "Icing." When iced, the drinker is required to get on one knee and chug the entire bottle, despite occasional jeers, jokes, discouragement and/or encouragement from onlookers." - Urbandictionary.com

Data.Name: Smirnoff Ice Peach Bellini
Data.Description: Smirnoff Ice Peach Bellini brings the fun, flavor and convenience of malt beverages to the world of champagne, with our Sparkling Seasonal malt beverage offering Smirnoff Ice Peach Bellini. A sophisticated blend of Peach with a hint of Raspberry. Yum!

Data.Name: Smirnoff Ice Grape
Data.Description: Here's a taste that's ripe for the pickin', so grab a bunch. Even though these grapes are wild - you shouldn't be - so drink responsibly.

Data.Name: Sixpoint Bengali IPA
Data.Description: American India Pale Ale (IPA)- 6.4% ABV. Pours a hazy caramel/copper color. Aromas of honey, citrus fruit, piney hops and sweet malts. Tastes of sweet malts with a strong caramel backbone. Bitter, citrusy hops are also prominent and add a zesty spiciness.

Data.Name: Reese's Pieces Candy
Data.Description: Grab a box of REESE'S Pieces Candy for big peanut butter taste in a crunchy candy shell. Perfect for on-the-go snacking and sharing on movie night.

Data.Name: Reese's Peanut Butter Cups
Data.Description: The classic combination of chocolate and peanut butter, REESE'S Peanut Butter Cups are the perfect companion for movies, sports and parties.

Data.Name: Reese's Crunchy Cookie Bar
Data.Description: What happens when crunchy cookie bits take up with the classic combo of chocolate and peanut butter? It’s a crunch-tastic celebration of taste! REESE’S Crunchy Cookie Big Cup is the perfect snack for all of life’s adventures.

Data.Name: Whatchamacallit Candy Bar
Data.Description: WHATCHAMACALLIT Candy Bar is the perfect blend of chocolate and chewy goodness. Enjoy delicious caramel covered in smooth milk chocolate.

Data.Name: Payday Candy Bar
Data.Description: Peanuts covered in creamy caramel, classic treat for everyone.

Data.Name: Reese's Crunchy Cookie Big Cup King Size
Data.Description: What happens when crunchy cookie bits take up with the classic combo of chocolate and peanut butter? It’s a crunch-tastic celebration of taste! REESE’S Crunchy Cookie Big Cup is the perfect snack for all of life’s adventures.

Data.Name: 3 Musketeers Bar
Data.Description: For a satisfyingly fluffy chocolate treat, look no further than 3 MUSKETEERS Sharing Size Candy Bars. Each 3 MUSKETEERS Sharing Size Chocolate Bar Pack is made of a light, whipped chocolate center enrobed in rich milk chocolate.

Data.Name: M&M's Milk Chocolate Candy
Data.Description: A snack favorite for chocolate lovers around the world. Made with real milk chocolate.

Data.Name: M&M's Peanut Butter Chocolate Candy
Data.Description: Iconic M&M'S Candy only gets better with the delicious taste of real peanut butter. Enjoy bite-sized pieces of chocolate-covered peanut butter that are coated with a colorful candy shell. Peanut Butter M&M'S Candy is a tasty chocolate treat that's great for parties, baking, road trips or filling your candy dish. Add colorful fun to your day with M&M’S Peanut Butter Chocolate Candy.

Data.Name: M&M's Caramel Chocolate Candy
Data.Description: Caramel lovers, rejoice! Introducing M&M'S Caramel Chocolate Candy, the first-ever soft and chewy M&M'S Candy. A soft caramel center is covered in rich milk chocolate and coated in a colorful crunchy candy shell for a fun, tasty treat.

Data.Name: Snickers Bar Almond
Data.Description: Try this candy bar containing delicious almonds. SNICKERS Almond Full Size Chocolate Bars are a delicious and unique candy that friends, family and party guests will love. Bring them to the office, use them in gift baskets or keep them on hand to pack in your lunch. With milk chocolate, almonds, caramel and nougat, SNICKERS Almond Singles Size Chocolate Candy Bars make a satisfying chocolate treat. Remember, you're not you when you're hungry.

Data.Name: Snickers Bar
Data.Description: The SNICKERS bar is an American classic, Crammed with peanuts, caramel and nougat then coated with milk chocolate. This hunger buster chocolate bar is packed with peanuts, chewy caramel and nougat, covered in delicious milk chocolate. Guaranteed to get you back to being you because “you're not you when you’re hungry”!

Data.Name: Snickers Bar Hazelnut
Data.Description: When you’re looking for a treat that really satisfies, look no further than SNICKERS Hazelnut Candy Bars. Simply imagine the classic SNICKERS Candy Bar ingredients you love. Now imagine hazelnut. There you have it, SNICKERS Hazelnut Candy Bar. Loaded with roasted hazelnuts, nougat, caramel and milk chocolate—and delicious whether simply unwrapped and enjoyed—SNICKERS Chocolate handles your hunger so that you can handle, well... anything.

Data.Name: Reese's Big Cup King
Data.Description: This one is for the true peanut butter lovers, who know you can never have enough REESE'S Creamy Peanut Butter. These cups are packed to the brim with flavor! Pick up the king size pack and find another peanut butter enthusiast to share with.

Data.Name: Reese's Big Cup Crunchy King
Data.Description: These big, crunchy peanut butter cups are a fun twist on a classic. Like crunchy peanut butter? Then these peanut-loaded cups are for you. Big Cups give you more delicious peanut butter in each bite.

Data.Name: Reese's Crispy Crunchy King Size Bar
Data.Description: Want a little nutty crunch to munch on? Get a bite of one of these. Made with REESE'S Creamy Peanut Butter, crunchy peanut candy and chopped peanuts, they’re a candy bar twist on REESE’S Peanut Butter Cups.

Data.Name: Reese's Pieces Peanut Butter King Cups
Data.Description: We put REESE'S Pieces Candy in REESE'S Peanut Butter Cups, and the internet lost its mind. It's a phenomenon only your taste buds can fully appreciate. Don’t deprive them. Get the king size, and share the CUPFUSION with a friend.

Data.Name: Hershey's Cookies N' Creme Bar
Data.Description: If you love chocolate (or cookies and cream ice cream), then you’ll appreciate the delicious combination of crunchy chocolate cookie bits and smooth white creme. HERSHEY'S Cookies 'n' Creme Candy Bars pack this classic flavor combo into each delicious bite.

Data.Name: Hershey's Milk Chocolate with Almonds Bar
Data.Description: Made from classic HERSHEY’S milk chocolate and crunchy almonds, these full-size chocolate bars are perfect when you want to stop and savor life’s sweeter side.

Data.Name: Hershey's Milk Chocolate Bar
Data.Description: Treat your friends, family, and yourself to the creamy, delicious taste of a HERSHEY'S Chocolate Bar. This versatile milk chocolate classic is perfect for savoring and sharing.

Data.Name: Trident Original
Data.Description: Chew On This With 30% fewer calories than sugared gum, less than 5 calories per stick, and a long-lasting flavor. Sugarless Trident Gum is an invigorating study aid, travel companion, or post-meal (or pre-date) refreshment. Sweetened with Xylitol, a naturally occurring substance, Original Flavor gum helps fight plaque and tooth decay.

Data.Name: Stride Spearmint Gum
Data.Description: Get fresh breath and long-lasting flavor with Stride Sugar Free Gum. Stride Gum keeps its texture and great taste thanks to the right balance of unique ingredients, flavors, and sweeteners. The refreshing blast of Spearmint flavor will keep you going at work, school--and everywhere else.

Data.Name: Stride Peppermint Gum
Data.Description: Get fresh breath and long-lasting flavor with Stride Sugar Free Gum. Stride Gum keeps its texture and great taste thanks to the right balance of unique ingredients, flavors, and sweeteners. The refreshing blast of Peppermint flavor will keep you going at work, school--and everywhere else. This order includes twelve 14-piece packs of Peppermint Stride Sugar Free Gum.

Data.Name: Ice Breakers Ice Cubes Peppermint Gum
Data.Description: Cooling flavor crystals release and icy blast of invigorating, long-lasting flavor with every chew.

Data.Name: Orbit Spearmint
Data.Description: Orbit White Spearmint Gum helps keep teeth white with a refreshing mint flavor for your most confident smile yet.

Data.Name: Bota Box Dry Rosé
Data.Description:
3L of rosé. Woohoo1
This rosé is crisp with aromas of raspberries and red rose and flavors of strawberry cake and grapefruit zest. Served well chilled, this wine pairs nicely with a variety of foods, including burgers, tacos, grilled chicken, and fruit & cheese plates. It's the perfect barbecue wine, the perfect beach wine, and the perfect picnic wine, but it's also the perfect sitting-around-watching-the-sunset wine.

Data.Name: Bota Box Old Vine Zinfandel
Data.Description: 3L of Zin! Dark and jammy with aromas of wild blackberry, plum and a hint of spice. Concentrated ripe stone fruit, dark berry flavors and toasted oak carry through to the palate for a long, lingering finish.

Data.Name: Big Smooth Old Vine Zinfandel
Data.Description: Big Smooth Zinfandel opens with bursting aromas of luscious black cherry, blackberry, fig, and framboise. Toasted coconut, Tahitian vanilla, and hints of smoked dill lift from the glass, as a result of American oak aging. Silky smooth on the palate with flavors of boysenberry, pomegranate reduction and red currants greeting you at first sip. On the mid-palate, fresh notes of coconut and vanilla bean float in and leave you with a balanced finish.

Data.Name: Beyra Grande Reserva Red
Data.Description:
Fruity aroma with very elegant and discreet minerality in balance with barrel ageing notes.
Berries, spices, subtle notes of vanilla and toast. Fruity and persistent with fresh and elegant aftertaste.

Data.Name: Beyra Reserva Quartz White
Data.Description: Very mineral and citrus, grapefruit, slightly smoky, vibrant acidity with a structure that promises good aging in the bottle.

Data.Name: Aperol
Data.Description:
Aperol is a classic Italian aperitif and key ingredient in Italy’s most popular cocktail, the Aperol Spritz. Its low alcohol content makes it perfect for daytime. Bright orange in color, its unique bittersweet taste is derived from sweet and bitter oranges, herbs and roots. It is a secret recipe that has remained unchanged, since its creation in 1919.

An Aperol Spritz is unforgettably delicious and the perfect way to enjoy a weekend brunch or after work drink with friends!

Data.Name: Absolut Ruby Red
Data.Description: Absolut Ruby Red is made exclusively from natural ingredients, and unlike some other flavored vodkas, it doesn’t contain any added sugar. Absolut Ruby Red is smooth and fruity with a crisp and refreshing character of zesty grapefruit.

Data.Name: Noble Vines 667 Pinot Noir
Data.Description: Noble Vines 667 Pinot Noir exhibits appealing aromas of black cherry, earth and a touch of vanilla. Plush tannins and balanced acidity support core flavors of ripe Bing cherry, bittersweet cocoa powder, and delicate hints of sage.

Data.Name: 14 Hands Merlot
Data.Description: Aromas of blackberries, plums and black cherries. Expressive flavors of cherries and berries are joined by subtle nuances of mocha and spice. Blackberries are repeated on the palate with notes of cherries and spice.

Data.Name: 14 Hands Cabernet Sauvignon
Data.Description: Concentrated aromas of dark stone fruits and toast burst from the glass. classic Cabernet Sauvignon flavors of black cherries with subtle hints of baking spice dance across the palate, bolstered by fine, round tannins. Its medium bodied wine is soft in mouth feel.

Data.Name: Woodford Reserve Master's Collection
Data.Description:
Aroma: Rich oak, overripe banana, and marzipan, with hints of orange oil, dusted graham cracker and dried cherry.

Taste: Dried apricot drizzled with rich dark chocolate layered over toasted hazelnuts and coffee with faint flavors of cinnamon and clove.

Finish: A long finish of spearmint and sweet cedar wood.

Data.Name: Oxley Gin
Data.Description: Oxley's is a smart new English gin, made using the extremely unusual 'cold distillation' technique. Cold distillation employs a vacuum to remove the pressure from within the still lowering the temperature to below -5°C, causing the spirit to ‘boil’.

Data.Name: Old Thompson American Whiskey
Data.Description: Old thompson american whiskey- Blended from the finest quality bourbons available. An excellent value. Dark gold with an amber cast. Moderately light-bodied. Notes of citrus, dried herbs, minerals. Flinty, lightly spiced impression with a slightly tangy fruity note. Vibrant finish.

Data.Name: Martini & Rossi Rosso Sweet Vermouth
Data.Description: Martini & Rossi Rosso Vermouth is a light, balanced and scarlet-hued Italian sweet red vermouth. This famous drink was first created by the Martini family in the ancient town of Pessione, nestling in the foothills of the Alps near Turin. The exquisite red vermouth has remained inextricably linked to the Italian passions of food, entertaining friends and motor racing, since 1863.

Data.Name: Martini & Rossi Dry Vermouth
Data.Description: Light and dry with a fresh sweetness. Floral bouquet greets the nose, leading to a fruity and tart palate of raspberries and lemons carried by a sparkling body. Perfect for a cocktail and food recipes!

Data.Name: Leblon Cachaca
Data.Description:
Clear with a faint straw hue. Sweet creamy vanilla pudding, light caramel, and spicy aromas. A smooth entry leads to an off-dry medium-full body of toasty coconut shavings, creamy vanilla, and brown spices. Finishes with a long, caramel, mineral, and white pepper fade. A very nice, vibrant-yet-mellow style. 

Leblon Cachaca was awarded a Double Gold Medal at the 7th Annual San Francisco World Spirits Competition. It was one of only two spirits in its category to receive the Double Gold Medal, and Leblon was also named 'Top Cachaca' by a judging panel of the most influential spirits industry professionals in the U.S.

Data.Name: Maker's 46 Bourbon Whisky
Data.Description: The first new Makers Mark recipe for at least 50 years, Maker's 46 is named for the number of different wood 'recipes' they tried before getting it right. Bottled at 47% it is matured in part in barrels containing a 'ladder' of toasted new French oak barrel staves to give more spice, sweetness and vanilla.

Data.Name: Louis Jadot Pouilly-Fuisse
Data.Description:
Maison Louis Jadot produces a Pouilly Fuissé with emerald gold tones which reflect a wine of finesse and distinction; the tasting is harmonious, fresh, full of flavors with hazelnuts, toasted almonds, grapefruit and lemon aromas.

It must be served rather cool and goes very well with shellfish, fish, white meat in cream sauce and poultry.

Pouilly Fuissé is pleasant to drink young, but can be aged in cellar a long time (5-8 years) to develop a superb complex bouquet.

Data.Name: Ledaig 10 Year Old Scotch Whisky
Data.Description: This extraordinary and distinguished hand-crafted single malt is the distillery’s signature smoky expression. For ten full years, oak wood casks lie in rest in ancient vaults. Within them, the aromatic Lochan waters commune with the peated malted barely to create a deep golden treasure that is both floral and smoky. Ledaig is one of our exquisite peated single malts, an integral part of the Tobermory family.

Data.Name: Jack Daniel’s Rye Whiskey
Data.Description: Introducing rye whiskey made Jack’s way. Crafted with our 70-percent rye grain bill, natural spring water from our own Cave Spring Hollow, and Jack’s time-honored charcoal mellowing process, Jack Daniel’s Tennessee Rye is a whiskey that could only come from Lynchburg, Tennessee. Master Distiller Jeff Arnett and the whiskey makers of the Jack Daniel Distillery have created a unique rye that’s undeniably spicy and complex yet sippin’ smooth. It might be one of our first new recipes in over 150-years, but if you know Jack, you’ll know Jack Daniel’s Tennessee Rye.

Data.Name: Jack Daniel's Single Barrel Select
Data.Description: "Made from our finest stocks of whiskey, bottled in the smallest of batches, just one barrel at a time, invites those who appreciate fine spirits to explore a range of unique whiskies that are exceptionally smooth and full of character."

Data.Name: Heineken Mini Keg
Data.Description: 5L. Euro Pale Lager- 5.0% ABV. Heineken is a full-bodied premium lager with deep golden color, light fruity aroma, a mild bitter taste and a balanced hop aroma leaving a crisp, clean finish for ultimate refreshing taste.

Data.Name: J Lohr Merlot
Data.Description: “The 2016 J. Lohr Estates Los Osos Merlot has a medium-dark color intensity with a mature red hue in the glass. Varietal aromas of black cherry and lilac are integrated with a barrel signature of toasted hazelnut, dark chocolate, and baking spice. We use whole berry fermentation and a generous amount of Malbec in this blend to accentuate bright fruit tones and provide a rich, lengthy finish.” - Steve Peck, Winemaker

Data.Name: Domaine Fournier Sancerre
Data.Description: "Domaine Fournier Pere et Fils Sancerre has clear, golden green reflections with aromas of syringa and blackcurrant. A touch of anise lingers with notes of gooseberries, grapefruit and crisp minerality."

Data.Name: Clayhouse Cabernet Sauvignon
Data.Description: The grape source is the Red Cedar Vineyard in Paso Robles. To create this wine, we utilized two different blocks of Cabernet Sauvignon fruit. The predominate block lies on a steep, sloping terrace of Rincon clay loam. It is unique, and features very well-drained soil, which must be heavily cover cropped for protection against erosion. The additional Cabernet Sauvignon fruit comes from a block which consists of fine sandy loam and is well-suited for growing wine grapes.

Data.Name: Barsol Pisco Supremo
Data.Description: A complex Mosto Verde Pisco, made in Peru from partially fermented grape must for a fruity spirit that's excellent neat.

Data.Name: Aria Portland Dry Gin
Data.Description: Aria is full bodied and boldly aromatic. Juniper is up front—obvious on the first nosing and initially on the palate. Underneath the juniper, there are layers of bright citrus, earthy undertones, floral highlights and subtle spicy notes reveal themselves--both on the nose and palate--though none are overpowering. All of the layers of flavor are balanced. The pristine Bull Run water use to cut Aria after distillation provides a rich, creamy mouthfeel. The finish is long and soft.

Data.Name: Grey Goose La Vanille
Data.Description: In crafting Grey Goose La Vanille Flavored Vodka, the nosing passes find only mild vanilla bean/vanilla extract aromas. The palate entry offers a genuine vanilla-like, bittersweet and spicy taste; the vanilla taste accelerates at midpalate and is appropriately bitter and tasty. Improved after a rocky beginning. 80 Proof Vodka

Data.Name: Grey Goose VX
Data.Description: Grey Goose VX is best enjoyed on the rocks in a fine snifter glass to appreciate its rich character and complex nose, with hints of white fruit blossom, plum, apricot, light citrus and wild honey, followed by a long lingering finish. It is truly unique and luxurious. Enjoy!

Data.Name: Twenty Rows Merlot
Data.Description: The Twenty Rows Merlot is an an intense, deeply, colored wine of concentrated aromas and flavors. Approachable and delicious The wine is full of dar cherries and black currants and has notes of cedar, sandalwood and coffee.

Data.Name: Sipsmith London Dry Gin
Data.Description: A traditional London Dry Gin distilled from the finest English Barley with ten carefully selected botanicals with a wonderful burst of juniper and a zesty, citrus freshness. Bold, complex and aromatic. Smooth enough for a Martini, but rich and balanced for a gin and tonic.

Data.Name: Briggs Original Boston Cranberry
Data.Description: Boston Cranberry is cold brewed with the best all natural ingredients and real fruit for a light, but flavorful spiked sparkling water.

Data.Name: Barone Fini Pinot Grigio
Data.Description:
This Pinot Grigio showcases aromas of floral and lemon mist with ripe juicy flavors of honeydew and apple filling the mouth.  Bright acidity balanced with warm minerality create a lingering crisp finish.

This incredibly versatile wine can be enjoyed alone, as an aperitif, or paired with a variety of cuisines such as seafood, pasta and poultry.

Data.Name: Barone Fini Merlot Trentino
Data.Description: Flavors of rich, ripe cherries and plums are enriched by the smooth, deep, well-structured background. A beautifully balanced wine with a long and velvety finish.

Data.Name: Ardbeg Uigeadail Single Malt Scotch Whisky
Data.Description: A heavily sherried Ardbeg bottled at cask strength. This is a marriage of ex-bourbon and ex-sherry casks, with a high proportion of ex-sherry casks. The Uigeadail name is from the river from which Ardbeg draws its water. A fantastic whisky, and probably the best value for money of their core range, even though it is very hard to pick from a line up so well stacked as Ardbegs.

Data.Name: Ardbeg 10 Year Old Scotch Whisky
Data.Description: A great gift for Ardbeg fans. This bottle of the distillery's 10-year-old single malt comes encased in a striking tin, modelled on Ardbeg's iconic warehouse which overlooks the Atlantic. The whisky itself is spicy, sweet and smoky, perfect for those who love peaty whisky.

Data.Name: Aberlour A'Bunadh Single Malt Scotch Whisky
Data.Description: Batch 62 of the A'Bunadh range - small batch bottlings of oloroso-sherry aged single malt - continues with this 61st edition, which as usual offers tasty notes of dried fruit, sherry, dark chocolate and spice.

Data.Name: 1800 Anejo Tequila
Data.Description: Made from 100% Agave and rested in oak for up to 3 years, this tequila has round finish. The aging gives this spirit aromas and flavors of toasted agave, caramel, ripe fruit, orange rinds with spicy undertones. This is the perfect tequila for sipping.

Data.Name: Captain Morgan Loconut
Data.Description: Captain Morgan is going "loco" this spring! Captain Morgan Loconut is an intensely delicious blend of caribbean rum, coconut liqueur, spice and natural flavors. this just may be the most delicious shot to hit the beach (or bar). Make sure to "smell the coco for a scent of loco" to enjoy our coconut-scented bottles.  For the captain’s gluten-intolerant crew members, you will be happy to know that Loconut is gluten free.

Data.Name: Bushmills Original Irish Whiskey
Data.Description: Bushmills Original Irish Whiskey is a whiskey crafted from a company that has been around for over four hundred years. The whiskey itself is mouth watering with notes of vanilla, honey, and dried fruit.

Data.Name: Crystal Head Vodka
Data.Description: Crystal Head vodka takes its inspiration from the legendary crystal skulls that are said to have come from the Aztec era and are believed to hold mystically powers.  The vodka itself is made in Newfoundland canada.

Data.Name: Coppola Silver Label Pinot Noir
Data.Description: This wine has exceptionally dark color, which is not typical of the varietal. It exhibits explosive aromatics and impressive concentration, due in large part to the well-draining soils of our Monterey vineyards. Tannins are supple and the finish on this wine is lengthy.

Data.Name: Mentos Pure Fresh Spearmint
Data.Description: Mentos Gum that delivers intense freshness that lasts chew after chew.

Data.Name: Mentos Pure Fresh Mint Gum
Data.Description: Mentos Gum that delivers intense freshness that lasts chew after chew.

Data.Name: Orbit Spearmint Gum
Data.Description: With Orbit Sugar Free Gum, there's no need to second-guess; you have the confidence to show the world what you're made of. The delicious Spearmint flavor gives you a clean and fresh mouth feeling so you're ready to seize your moment when it comes. Time to Shine.

Data.Name: Eclipse Spearmint Gum
Data.Description: Get incredibly fresh breath whenever you need it with Eclipse sugar-free gum. Crunch into the minty outer shell and release a cool burst of refreshing spearmint-flavored gum. Keep a pack in your pocket or a cup in your car so you'll always have breath freshening on hand to share

Data.Name: Eclipse Winterfrost Gum
Data.Description: Get incredibly fresh breath whenever you need it with Eclipse Sugar free Gum. Crunch into the minty outer shell and release a cool burst of refreshing Winterfrost flavored gum. Keep a pack in your pocket or a cup in your car so you'll always have breath freshening on hand to share.

Data.Name: Kit Kat
Data.Description: Be all about those breaks. And the best breaks start with these classic bars of crispy wafers coated in smooth milk chocolate.

Data.Name: Twix
Data.Description: With crunchy cookie, smooth caramel, and creamy chocolate to savor twice each time, TWIX® allows you to make whatever you’re doing more fun.

Data.Name: Butterfinger Share Pack
Data.Description: Butterfinger bars offer the classic Butterfinger experience of a crispety, crunchety, peanut-buttery center covered in chocolaty goodness!

Data.Name: Hendrick's Midsummer Solstice
Data.Description:
Hendrick’s Midsummer Solstice is a delightfully floral gin that is a lighter and more crisp take on the Hendrick's house style, making it perfect for day-casions such as brunch and enjoying the summertime. 

Tasting Notes: Lush flora coupled with the unmistakable Hendrick’s signature cucumber & rose finish.

Data.Name: Gosling's Ginger Beer
Data.Description: Now, making a delicious Dark ‘n Stormy is a breeze. As always, start with two ounces of deep, rich Gosling’s Black Seal Rum in a tall ice-filled glass. Then, top with Gosling's perfectly balanced ginger beer; the only ginger beer created strictly to make Dark ‘n Stormy cocktails.

Data.Name: Glenrothes Maker's Cut Scotch Whisky
Data.Description: The Whisky Maker's Cut expression from Glenrothes' Soleo Collection is completely matured in first-fill sherry seasoned casks, resulting in punchy notes of orange, cinnamon and dried fruit. The whole range is named after the process of sun-drying grapes in preparation for sherry production, hence the particularly heavy focus on sherry throughout the series.

Data.Name: Glenrothes 12 Year Scotch Whisky
Data.Description:
A Glenrothes 12 Year Old in classic style: fruity and sweet. Aged solely in sherry-seasoned casks, this Speyside whisky has notes of vanilla, melon, banana and cinnamon.

This 12-year-old whisky is part of The Soleo Collection: a range of five whiskies from The Glenrothes, ranging from 10 to 25 years old, which pay homage to the grapes from which some sherries, such as Pedro Ximénez, are made.

Data.Name: Appleton Estate Reserve Blend Rum
Data.Description: Appleton Estate Reserve Blend was introduced in 2016 as part's of the brand's relaunched range. Replacing the eight year old, and with a similar profile this is a sweet, smooth sipper that lends itself very well to quality cocktails.

Data.Name: Angel's Envy Bourbon Whiskey
Data.Description: Angel’s Envy Kentucky Straight Bourbon is finished in port wine casks for an award-winning spirit. Angel's Envy guides each batch’s conditioning, blending their handcrafted bourbon in small batches of 8 to 12 barrels at a time. It’s typically aged for up to 6 years.

Data.Name: Disaronno Originale Amaretto Liqueur
Data.Description: Disaronno is a versatile spirit featuring an original taste and unmistakable aroma. The recipe, passed down from one generation to the next, dates back to 1525 and continues to be produced by the Reina Family in Saronno, Italy. Enjoy delicious cocktails or on the rocks.

Data.Name: Aberfeldy 12 Year Old Single Malt Scotch Whisky
Data.Description: A fruity, clean and polished malt with a touch of honey and spice, Aberfeldy 12 Year Old is an excellent introduction to this Highland distillery. Aberfeldy's main claim to fame is as the heart of the excellent Dewar's blend but whiskies like this are putting it firmly in the spotlight.

Data.Name: Deanston 12 Year Scotch Whiskey
Data.Description: Dry and nutty, with light peat, lemon grass and leather flavors. Mouth feel is slightly oily. Finishes smooth with lemon-zest and lightly malty with nutty dryness.

Data.Name: Che Gaucho Chardonnay
Data.Description:
Ché Gaucho Chardonnay delivers a smooth, rich flavor of melon and green apples with light notes of butter. Oak spice emerges toward the finish.

Pair this wine with a nice chicken risotto, ceviche, or lobster bisque.

Data.Name: Carpano Antica Formula Vermouth
Data.Description: "WITH ITS UNMISTAKABLE TASTE AND AN INCREASINGLY INTERNATIONAL FOLLOWING, THE ITALIAN VERMOUTH PAR EXCELLENCE IS IDEAL FOR MAKING REFINED, EXCLUSIVE COCKTAILS." -Carpano

Data.Name: Canadian LTD Whiskey
Data.Description: Golden amber color. Golden raisin, dried apple, and toffee aromas. A soft gentle entry leads to an off-dry light body of caramel and white nut flavors with a quick fudge and caramel fade. The 5th largest selling U.S. bottled Canadian Whisky. Made from 100% aged Canadian Whiskies.

Data.Name: Cabo Wabo Reposado Tequila
Data.Description: Created by Sammy Hager of Van Halen -- this tequila is made of 100% blue Agave. The process includes aging in oak barrels and fine-tuning the fermented juice to create a flavor filled smooth style to be enjoyed the Cabo Wabo way.

Data.Name: Cabo Wabo Anejo Tequila
Data.Description: Created by Sammy Hager of Van Halen this tequila is made of 100% Blue Agave. Aged in an oak barrel this rich and refined anejo is presented in a unique hand-blown artisan glass bottle.

Data.Name: Bully Boy Whiskey
Data.Description: "When thinking about our favorite whiskeys, we kept coming back to balance. Too often whiskey is characterized by extremes: Bourbon being too sweet or Rye being too dry. Our goal was to create a spirit that captured the essence of each without relying too heavily on one. That’s why our mash bill features corn, which imparts a sweet, bourbon-like overtone, complemented with a healthy dose of rye, which imparts a dry, spicy undertone." - Bully Boy Distillers

Data.Name: Skittles Original
Data.Description: Bite-size, colorful chewy candies Taste the rainbow. Original bold fruit flavors include orange, lemon, green apple, grape and strawberry. Ideal for parties, game-time snacks or even as a topping for your favorite dessert. Rainbow of Skittles makes your taste buds sit up and say "Wow".

Data.Name: Skittles Wild Berry
Data.Description: Loaded with wild berry flavors, these Skittles cannot be tamed. Get wild with berry punch, strawberry, melon berry, wild cherry, and raspberry flavors.

Data.Name: Skittles Sweets & Sours
Data.Description: Taste The Rainbow - Sweets & Sours include sour cherry, sour blue raspberry, sour watermelon, sweet orange and sweet strawberry flavors.

Data.Name: Skittles Brightside Share Size
Data.Description: Unicorns really do exist. They have to, right? Because how else can you explain the big fruit flavors packed into every bite-size Skittles candy? There's magic afoot here, people. It's a taste sensation that makes even the most stoic of unicorns smile. So, in summary, unicorns, which exist, really like Skittles candies. And you will too. Taste the Rainbow.

Data.Name: Starburst Gummies Sours
Data.Description:
Starburst sour-packed, fruit-flavored gummies that keep you coming back for more. Perfect candies for parties, sweet snacking, and anytime you want a burst of fruity flavor
Starburst Gummies Sours candies contain cherry, strawberry, blue raspberry, and watermelon flavors. These gummy candies are soft, chewy, and oh-so irresistible!

Data.Name: Starburst Minis
Data.Description: Small things can actually be pretty great. Want proof? Check out these Starburst Minis. They're just like the Starburst candy you know and love, only smaller and unwrapped. Starburst candies are packed with a variety of great-tasting fruit flavors and a deliciously soft, chewy texture to be enjoyed anytime, anywhere. Like, say, right now. Or right…now.

Data.Name: Starburst Originals
Data.Description: Bursting with refreshing fruit flavors. Unexplainably juicy, Starburst Original Fruit Chews are packed with four great tasting fruit flavors including Cherry, Orange, Lemon and Strawberry.

Data.Name: Starburst FaveREDS
Data.Description: Have you experienced the unexpectedly juicy burst of bold fruit flavor inside every Starburst candy? Treat yourself to the extraordinary juiciness that defines these beloved chewy candies. From Starburst candies right out of the wrapper to Starburst recipes and decorations, there are endless ways to add a burst of juicy flavor every day, including adding them to your next party. Package includes 14 ounce bag of STARBURST FaveREDs Fruit hew Candy.

Data.Name: Reese's Pieces Peanut Butter Cups
Data.Description: Enjoy the crunch of REESE’S Pieces Candy stuffed inside the smooth perfection of REESE’S Peanut Butter Cups. This mashup lives up to the hype.

Data.Name: Hershey's Cookies N' Creme King Size
Data.Description: HERSHEY’S Cookies ‘n’ Creme Bars are a unique twist on a classic flavor combination. Enjoy crunchy chocolate cookies and smooth white creme, in King Size!

Data.Name: Twix Peanut Butter
Data.Description:
It's a twist on the original that only Left Twix® could pull off. A crunchy, flavorful cookie with creamy peanut butter and milk chocolate. Enjoy this unique combination and be weary of peanut butter look-alikes, like those from Right Twix®.

It's a distinct take on the original that only Right Twix® could create. Milk chocolate, smooth peanut butter and a crispy, delectable cookie. Savor this special blend and watch for peanut butter fakers, like those ringers at Left Twix®.

Data.Name: Wrigley's Doublemint Gum
Data.Description: "Double Your Pleasure, Double Your Fun." Enjoy the refreshing taste of Doublemint gum—the unique, minty flavor you can't get anywhere else.

Data.Name: Orbit White Spearmint Gum
Data.Description: Be cool and confident with the refreshing mint flavor of Orbit Spearmint Gum.

Data.Name: Orbit White Peppermint Gum
Data.Description: Orbit White Peppermint Gum helps keep teeth white* with a burst of minty flavor for your most confident smile yet.

Data.Name: Little Book Whiskey
Data.Description:
Appearance: Bright copper 

Nose: A very sweet-and-savory nose. I get salted peanuts, fresh corn, sherry, almonds, wood shavings, white wine, caramel corn, and the scent that rises from a fresh loaf of multigrain bread. There’s also banana, coconut, caramel, and brazil nut, kind of like a fancy tropical torte served at a Hawaiian resort.

Palate: A syrupy mouth feel introduces sweet waves of citrus, tropical fruits, white peaches, fresh grain, creamy caramel, and strong vanilla. Tingly spice enters at the mid-palate, with cinnamon Red Hots and clove-studded orange. The finish is likewise sweet and a little sticky, with a hearty wallop of alcohol.

Data.Name: 5 Gum RPM Mint
Data.Description: Truth or dare. Choose a stick. Take a chance. 35% fewer calories than sugared gum. Calorie content of this size piece has been reduced from 8 to 5 calories.

Data.Name: Chateau d'Oupia Minervois Rosé
Data.Description: Chateau d’Oupia Minervois rosé is another one of those French names that sounds like a mouthful. Actually, it is a mouthful. Oupia is made with syrah grapes from the famous Minervois appellation in southern France. (I’m pretty sure "rosé" is French for “summer wine.”) Don’t let the salmon-pink color fool you — under the surface lies a rich backbone of the dark fruit from which it is made.

Data.Name: Billette Côtes de Provence Rosé
Data.Description: A gorgeous rosé from France. Billette has apricot tones with floral aromas, complete with berry fruit flavors. 13% ABV

Data.Name: Notorious Pink Rosé
Data.Description: Some say a Rosé shouldn’t be to be too pink, but Notorious Pink begs to differ. This Rosé is pale pink in color that exudes floral orange blossom aromas. Made from 100% Grenache from the South of France, mature berries balance the flavors of ripe berries that give it a wonderful acidity and soft minerality.

Data.Name: Duggan's Irish Cream
Data.Description: Duggan's Irish Cream is carefully crafted with fresh Irish cream, premium Irish spirits and the finest Irish whiskey. Duggan's Irish Cream Liqueur was created at Duggan's Dairy Farm near Waterford Ireland. The farm is no more but luckily the recipe survived and is just as smooth creamy and delicious now as it was originally. Take time to savor this very special Irish cream liqueur.

Data.Name: Leroux Peppermint Schnapps
Data.Description: Leroux Peppermint Schnapps is a strong, dry peppermint-flavored spirit. Made from all natural herbs and spices.

Data.Name: Leroux Anisette
Data.Description: Leroux Anisette is a delicious after-dinner drink, its sweet black licorice flavor comes from the aniseed.

Data.Name: Bacardi Pineapple Fusion Rum
Data.Description: A unique fusion of pineapple and coconut rums.

Data.Name: Baileys Vanilla Cinnamon
Data.Description: This versatile blend of Madagascar Vanilla and cinnamon is a unique experience perfect for cocktails and shots.

Data.Name: Baileys Salted Caramel
Data.Description: Delight in the luxurious taste of Irish Cream liqueur artfully blended with rich caramel and a hint of salt for a truly irresistible taste from Baileys. Share the spirit and enjoy with others.

Data.Name: DeKuyper Buttershots Butterscotch Schnapps
Data.Description: Dekuyper liqueur infused with all natural, intense butterscotch flavors. The nose is warm and buttery, with a rich melted butterscotch palate. Mix with Irish Cream for a delicious buttery nipple. A fan favorite.

Data.Name: Frangelico
Data.Description: Frangelico envelops the senses, drawing you in and providing a refreshing flavorful experience. The senses delight in the beauty of Italy, the sweetness of the taste and smoothness of the texture, all encased in an intriguing bottle. Discover Frangelico’s inner sweetness here.

Data.Name: Alizé Peach
Data.Description: Intensely unique and inviting, Alizé Peach is a succulent infusion of ripe, luscious peaches delicately blended with premium French Vodka. Alizé Peach Passion is a full bodied liqueur that is smooth and favorably sweet on the palate.

Data.Name: Alizé Red Passion
Data.Description:
Alizé Red Passion expertly blends the alluring flavor of ripe, exotic passion fruit and the all-natural juices of fresh, tangy cranberries with premium French Vodka.  This luscious fusion is remarkably balanced with sweet, vivid passion fruit and crisp, tart cranberries.

Alizé Red Passion’s distinct and delicious flavors can be savored on the rocks or in unique, colorful cocktails like the Party Crasher.

Data.Name: Alizé Gold Passion
Data.Description:
L’ Original.  Alizé Gold Passion delicately blends the intensely flavored and aromatic juices of the exotic passion fruit with premium French vodka.  The result is a liqueur that is exceptionally smooth and favorably sweet with vivid passion fruit flavor.

Alizé Gold Passion’s distinct and delicious flavors can be savored on the rocks or in unique, colorful cocktails like the Golden Margarita.

Data.Name: 99 Grapes Schnapps
Data.Description: An explosion of grape flavor, straight from the vine.

Data.Name: 99 Coconuts Schnapps
Data.Description: The beach is in reach with this aromatic, luscious, tropical sensation.

Data.Name: 99 Apples Schnapps
Data.Description: Intense tangy apple taste that makes Apple Martinis exceptional, it's apple to the core. It's classic! Sweet, succulent, and intensely apple.

Data.Name: 99 Watermelons Schnapps
Data.Description: 99 Watermelon Schapps Liquer is a fun, full flavored. Great as shooters or as ingredients in mixed drinks, with a taste intensity that stands up to vodka and mixers. You bring the picnic basket, this brings the watermelons.

Data.Name: 99 Bananas Schnapps
Data.Description:
Banana-flavored schnapps. Intense banana flavor, fruity, tropical yet smooth, refreshing, easy to drink and easy to mix in delicious cocktails like chocolate banana martinis and tropical punch!

Taste the sweet tropics and let your imagination take over.

Data.Name: Tequila Rose Strawberry Cream
Data.Description: Tequila Rose is the original strawberry cream liqueur. Combining tequila with strawberry cream was a bold innovation, the first drink of its kind to pair cream with anything other than Irish whiskey. Exotic. Unexpected. Delicious. Over twenty years later, Tequila Rose remains the world’s best-selling strawberry cream liqueur and was the inspiration that paved the way for the unique cream liqueurs that have followed.

Data.Name: Camarena Reposado Tequila
Data.Description: Aged in oak barrels for 60 days. Soft and smooth on the palate imparting flavors of vanilla and caramel onto Camarena’s natural agave sweetness and notes of soft spice. Sweet toasted agave, soft spice. Soft and smooth on the palate and soft finish with lingering vanilla and caramel.

Data.Name: Camarena Silver Tequila
Data.Description: Notes of toasted agave, fresh green herbs and vibrant citrus. Soft and smooth on the palate with hints of sweet vanilla, savory brown spices, and black pepper with a warming finish. Fresh green herbs, vibrant citrus and sweet vanilla, with soft warming finish, savory brown spices and black pepper.

Data.Name: Lunazul Blanco Tequila
Data.Description: This is tequila in its wildest, most natural state, crystal clear and un-aged, allowing its 100% agave flavor to take the lead. Exceptionally smooth and balanced with bright color and silver highlights. Refreshing fruity nose exhibiting tropical and apple notes with a healthy dose of salt and citrus, similar to that of fresh agave. The palate is semi-viscous and peppery with ripe fruit tones giving way to crisp citrus notes and a hint of vanilla. Wonderfully balanced finish with long lasting citrusy, peppery, and herbaceous notes.

Data.Name: Lunazul Reposado Tequila
Data.Description: 100% agave tequila that’s “rested” in Bourbon barrels for smooth, rich flavor. Bright, golden color with subtle oak and vanilla notes. The nose is delicate and fruity offering aromatics reminiscent of baked or grilled pineapple, but is best identified as pure, baked agave. Lush caramel with layers of semi-sweet vanilla, fruit and spice evolving to subtle oak and vanilla notes. Long and creamy finish with lingering smoky and spicy notes.

Data.Name: Milagro Reposado
Data.Description: Milagro Reposado is made from 100% estate-grown, hand picked blue agave harvested from the highlands of Jalisco. Milagro's triple distillation process produces tequila of extraordinary depth and character for unparalleled smoothness. Although Reposados are typically aged for two months, Milagro Anejo is aged in American oak whiskey barrels for six months in small, handmade batches for a mellowed taste and pleasing bouquet.

Data.Name: Glenfiddich Original Scotch Whisky
Data.Description:
While most whiskies today mature in oak, sherry casks were more prominent in 1963. The result, then and now, is a spirit contrasting many of Glenfiddich's other expressions.

The aroma is floral with the hallmark Glenfiddich pear, followed by lively fruit notes, biscuity with a soft vanilla oakiness and deliciously dry finish.

Data.Name: Glenlivet 12 Year Old First Fill Exclusive
Data.Description: This is the first ever limited edition release of The Glenlivet First Fill in the US. A Unique 12-year-old matured in first fill American oak casks.

Data.Name: Buchanan's Black & White Scotch Whisky
Data.Description: Famous old blend containing a high proportion of quality grain whisky. James Buchanan apparently got the idea for the brand on his way home from a dogshow - and the rest is history.

Data.Name: Glenlivet 15 Year Old Scotch Whiskey
Data.Description: The 15 Year Old is deep gold in colour, and leaves behind traces of sweet almond and spice. French Limousin Oak cask and flavors of sweet fruits and delicate spice.

Data.Name: Glenlivet 21 Year Old Scotch Whiskey
Data.Description: The epitome of discernment, the qualities of this 21-year matured whisky are not just rare… they’re unique. American Oak and ex-Sherry Oak cask with full-bodied, warming, dried fruits, spice flavors.

Data.Name: Glenlivet 18 Year Old Scotch Whiskey
Data.Description: Balanced, rich and elegant, this is a whisky for special occasions. First and Second Fill American Oak and ex-Sherry casks and a ripe citrus, winter spice taste.

Data.Name: Captain Morgan Cannon Blast
Data.Description: Captain Morgan’s Cannon Blast Spiced Rum is an intensely delicious shot that is citrus sweet with a spark of heat. The sweet citrus delivers a pleasing and delicious front end, while providing a finish with a warming (but not overwhelming) sensation. Not into shots? No problem. You won't be disappointed in using Cannon Blast in one of your favorite cocktails.

Data.Name: Captain Morgan Long Island Iced Tea
Data.Description: A legendary mix of rum, vodka, whiskey, gin and triple-sec liqueur with a refreshing taste only the Captain could deliver.

Data.Name: Salignac VS Cognac
Data.Description: A distinct blend of young cognacs before aging for a unique and extremely smooth cognac. Soft flavors of vanilla and caramel with a great balance of oak and subtle spice. Enjoy neat or on the rocks

Data.Name: Club Caribe Banana Rum
Data.Description: Club Caribe Banana Rum is a full-flavored, tropical rum that is distilled to 55 proof creating a full bodied tropical cocktail. Great for mixing your favorite drinks.

Data.Name: Captain Morgan Parrot Bay Strawberry Rum
Data.Description: A luscious summer berry flavor infused with a fruity twist. Clear in appearance, this 42 proof rum will bring out the feeling of summer fun and Caribbean life no matter where you sip it. Simply mix with lemonade and pour over ice for a delicious island cocktail.

Data.Name: Captain Morgan Parrot Bay Pineapple
Data.Description: The fruity bouquet consists of plump aromas of sweetened coconut and bubble gum sugar onto the olfactory sense. Taste is all coconut with nary a trace of rum at first, then turns rich, creamy, and properly sweet.

Data.Name: Captain Morgan Grapefruit Rum
Data.Description: A ripe, juicy and ruby red grapefruit profile balanced with background notes of molasses and tropical fruit. Slightly tart with natural fruit flavors that yield a refreshingly crisp finish. a summer’s sunset in a bottle.

Data.Name: Captain Morgan Pineapple Rum
Data.Description: Very fragrant fresh pineapple aroma, with a ripe & juicy pineapple taste profile. Its slight notes of molasses and natural fruit flavors help to create a balanced finish that is both perfectly sweet and refreshingly crisp. The result is a delicious cocktail as lively as a midsummer three-day weekend.

Data.Name: Potter's 151 Rum
Data.Description: Potter's 151 is a lively, spirity rum that almost has a life of its own. It is great as a mixer with cola.

Data.Name: Bacardi Pina Colada
Data.Description: Ready-made Pina Colada cocktail from Bacardi. It combines pineapple, coconut and Bacardi Superior rum. It's designed to be easily served, just simply pour over crushed ice in a tall glass.

Data.Name: Bacardi Zombie
Data.Description: A refreshing mix of Bacardi rum and quality ingredients make this ready to serve drink. Just open and pour over ice. Sweet rum, pineapple, lime, orange and apricot flavors.

Data.Name: Bacardi Black Rum
Data.Description: Bacardi Black rum is a medium-bodied black rum, crafted with passion by the Maestros de Ron Bacardí. Its rich, dark flavors develop in heavily charred oak barrels and are shaped through a secret blend of charcoals. Some might call it black magic.

Data.Name: Bacardi Grapefruit Rum
Data.Description: A white rum infused with pink grapefruit flavors for a refreshing sour and semi-sweet taste. Add Bacardi Grapefruit rum to a Mojito or a Mule, and experience the sweet citrus flavor of pink grapefruit. You'll wonder why you never thought of it before.

Data.Name: Bacardi Mango Rum
Data.Description: A fusion of juicy mango with an unmistakable citrus zing of orange gives Bacardi Mango rum its unique character and flavor. Once you've tasted it, you will never forget it.

Data.Name: Bacardi Lime Rum
Data.Description: Intense, refreshing lime flavor that radiates on the taste buds with aromas of lime zest and glistening bright citrus notes. If an impromptu beach party had a flavor – Bacardi Lime would be it. Our expertly blended Bacardi Lime rum delivers the zest. Simply add it to your favorite beverage and let the dancing begin!

Data.Name: Bacardi Pineapple Rum
Data.Description: Bacardi Pineapple rum is a unique fusion of naturally fresh pineapple and white rum. Open a bottle and take your taste buds on a trip to the tropics, without ever leaving your own back yard.

Data.Name: Evan Williams Bourbon
Data.Description: Evan Williams Bourbon is full of character and simply done right. Named after Evan Williams, who opened Kentucky’s First Distillery along the banks of the Ohio River in 1783, it’s aged far longer than required by law. The result is a Bourbon that’s smooth, rich, and easy to enjoy. The taste has notes of oak, brown sugar and caramel. 86 proof.

Data.Name: Evan Williams Honey
Data.Description: Evan Williams Honey combines the smoothness of our Straight Kentucky Bourbon with the sweetness of real, natural honey. Go on, give it a shot. 70 proof with sweet honey and allspice, vanilla and a hint of smoke notes.

Data.Name: J. Seeds Apple Cider Whiskey
Data.Description: J. Seeds Apple Cider Whiskey is a flavor explosion. A perfect blend of cinnamon, fresh apples, and a slight kick of soft spice. This is the perfect drink to pair with any fall meal, or in a frozen drink.

Data.Name: Jack Daniel's Gentleman Jack
Data.Description: Inspired by the original gentleman distiller and founder, Gentleman Jack undergoes a second charcoal mellowing to achieve exceptional smoothness. Its balanced flavor is perfect for celebrating life’s extraordinary occasions, plus all the moments along the way.

Data.Name: Jack Daniel's Tennessee Honey
Data.Description: A blend of Jack Daniel’s Tennessee Whiskey and a unique honey liqueur, for a taste that’s one-of-a-kind and unmistakably Jack. With hints of honey and a finish that’s naturally smooth, Jack Daniel’s Tennessee Honey offers a taste of the unexpected.

Data.Name: Kern Triple Irish Whiskey
Data.Description: 40% ABV kern is made from the best Irish malts and grains. The whiskey is distilled in pot stills blended and then aged in american oak for 3 to 5 years. Tasting notes a good balance of sweet and dry providing a framework for flavors to emerge. Well structured with honey notes hanging from the nose. Sweet rich mellow with soft spices at the end.

Data.Name: The Knot Irish Whiskey
Data.Description: The Knot 100 proof whiskey has a spicy, oaky nose that has a hint of vanilla. Strong taste with a smooth spicy finish. Typically served as a shot. Gold Medal San Francisco World Spirits Competition '07.

Data.Name: Chloe Prosecco
Data.Description: Chloe Prosecco defines the elegant sparkling style for which this captivating area is known. This wine is bursting with fresh fruit and fine bubbles, with notes of peach, green apple, citrus and white flowers on the nose and palate.

Data.Name: Chloe Pinot Noir
Data.Description: An elegant yet complex Pinot Noir that delivers flavors and aromas of wild strawberry, plum, cherries, and a hint of spicy clove. A versatile wine, this Pinot Noir complements meals of salmon, lamb, poultry and grilled vegetables.

Data.Name: Chloe Pinot Grigio
Data.Description: On the palate, this Pinot Grigio displays flavors of juicy white peach, soft melon, crisp apple and floral honeysuckle with a subtle undertone of Meyer lemon.

Data.Name: Cavit Riesling Minis
Data.Description: No other white varietal rivals Riesling's magical blend of exhilarating aromas, ripe fruit flavors, refreshing acidity and versatile compatibility with food. The cool northern Italian climate in which Cavit's vineyards are planted provides excellent growing conditions for this beguiling white grape.

Data.Name: Cavit Riesling
Data.Description: No other white varietal rivals Riesling's magical blend of exhilarating aromas, ripe fruit flavors, refreshing acidity and versatile compatibility with food. The cool northern Italian climate in which Cavit's vineyards are planted provides excellent growing conditions for this beguiling white grape.

Data.Name: Cavit Pinot Noir
Data.Description:
With a distinctive balance with bright cherry notes and hints of red berries, it is big, bold, and complex.

Enjoy with grilled or roasted red meats, poultry, flavorful vegetarian entrees, risottos. Enjoy with fish such as salmon, tuna and swordfish.

Data.Name: Cavit Pinot Noir Minis
Data.Description:
With a distinctive balance with bright cherry notes and hints of red berries, it is big, bold, and complex.

Enjoy with grilled or roasted red meats, poultry, flavorful vegetarian entrees, risottos. Enjoy with fish such as salmon, tuna and swordfish.

Data.Name: Cavit Pinot Grigio Minis
Data.Description: The wine shows in the glass with tart lemon notes, unripe nectarines, subtle pineapple and a touch of marzipan. Its sharp acidity makes it quenchable on its own or with green bean almondine next to a grilled white fish.

Data.Name: Cavit Merlot Minis
Data.Description:
With its ruby red color and round notes of plum, red cherry and a hint of chocolate, it’s a varietal that thrives in Trentino’s environment.

A perfect companion to grilled meats and most full-flavored dishes. Serve at room temperature.

Data.Name: Cavit Merlot
Data.Description:
With its ruby red color and round notes of plum, red cherry and a hint of chocolate, it’s a varietal that thrives in Trentino’s environment.

A perfect companion to grilled meats and most full-flavored dishes. Serve at room temperature.

Data.Name: Southern Comfort 100
Data.Description: A premium whiskey that's bold and balanced, with core whiskey notes and vibrant caramel and fruit accents. Crafted for true whiskey lovers who want a little extra New Orleans kick whether enjoyed neat, on the rocks or mixed in classic cocktails.

Data.Name: Seagram's 7 Crown Dark Honey Whiskey
Data.Description: Seagram's 7 with honey is a blend of Seagram's 7 Crown American blended whiskey dosed with honey and spices. The smooth blend starts with full-bodied character of great American whiskey, which is then finished with a whisper of raw American honey creating an exceptionally smooth and delicious taste experience. Perfect on its own or mixed, tempt your guests with a chilled shot or combine with cola over ice.

Data.Name: Seagram's V.O. Whiskey
Data.Description: Seagram's VO is a classic Canadian whisky blend, made with spirit of at least 6 years of age. It is spicy and creamy, medium-bodied with honey, caramel and coffee and a touch of orange marmalade and pannacotta.

Data.Name: Seagram's American Spiced Whiskey
Data.Description: Seagram's 7 Crown ushers in a new era with Seagram's 7 Crown Spiced, a 71 proof blended whiskey made of aged bourbon with hints of spices. Seagram's 7 Crown Spiced tastes great on its own, on the rocks, or in your favorite cocktail.

Data.Name: Old Crow Bourbon
Data.Description: Old Crow Bourbon Whiskey is sweet and light, with vanilla and caramel notes; crisp and light finish.

Data.Name: Cadée Deceptivus Bourbon Whiskey
Data.Description:
First matured as "Straight Bourbon Whiskey" in new American Oak barrels, then double-barrel
finished in French Oak Casks previously used for aging rich, 20 year old Port in Portugal.
​
With an aroma rich in port, cocoa, dark cherries, toffee, chocolate and mature oak on the palate, the concentration of flavors is inimitable.

Data.Name: Jefferson's Reserve Bourbon Whiskey
Data.Description: Jefferson’s Reserve is a big, sophisticated bourbon that has a lot of flavor up front, a lot of weight mid palate and a deep, wonderful finish.

Data.Name: Knob Creek Kentucky Straight Bourbon Whiskey
Data.Description: An unflinching balance of deep, old-style flavor with a natural oak sweetness. 100 proof.

Data.Name: Pavão Vinho Verde Rosé
Data.Description: A rose color with orange highlights and the aroma of grapes and strawberries. Fresh, delicate acidity and smooth strawberries. Fruity, elegant and with a good finish. Drink young, ideally till one year and a half after the harvest. Pairs well with seafood, appetizers and light dishes.

Data.Name: Dewar's Highlander Honey Scotch Whisky
Data.Description: Dewar's created a scotch that is an infusion of distilled heather honey into the original Dewar's White Label Blended Scotch whisky. Enjoy on the rocks or mixed with cola.

Data.Name: William Lawson's
Data.Description: Nothing should come between a man and our whisky. No peaty overtones. No smoky aroma. No bouncer saying you’re wearing the wrong shoes. Nothing to stop you enjoying its big, bold fruity flavour. Its taste of toasted cereal. Hint of juicy apple. And dollop of chewy toffee. But don’t just take our word, take a sip. Or two.

Data.Name: McClelland's Highland
Data.Description: A malty, spicy, well-balanced flavour, with a very smooth mouth-filling aftertaste, this is a truly satisfying malt. Malt with a dry peated nose and hints of cinnamon and hazelnut.

Data.Name: Vina Robles Rosé
Data.Description:
Vinaa Robles Rosé is inspired by the refreshing, dry rosés of southern France. With its sunsoaked slopes and coastal ambiance, Paso Robles boasts an ideal terroir for echoing the flavor and spirit of these popular Mediterranean wines.

Tasting Notes:
Red cherry and pomegranate - rose petals - lively finish

Data.Name: Sensi 18k Moscato Rosé
Data.Description: 18K Rose' is made by Moscato, it has a light shining pink colour, exalted by fine persistent bubbling, an intense nose and a fresh, fruity and fragrant taste of white flowers petals and strawberries. A very stylish gift to give.   Charming and seductive with its beautiful pink bottle, it is ideal for framing the most romantic moments or for a fine cocktail.

Data.Name: Rosatello Sparkling Rosé
Data.Description: This brilliantly pink sparkling rosé and its aromas of wild strawberries will remind you of a summer afternoon. Linger over refreshing flavors of sweet raspberries artfully balanced with bright acidity and a fresh, pleasing finish. Tapster recommends chilling before enjoying.

Data.Name: Ole Smoky Moonshine Apple Pie
Data.Description: Moonshine is as American as apple pie. So it only made sense to blend pure apple juice, ground cinnamon, and other spices with whiskey to create Ole Smoky Apple Pie Moonshine. This delicious combination of flavors can conjure up memories of warm apple pie on a cool summer evening and goes down just as easy. 70 proof.

Data.Name: Paul Mas Rosé
Data.Description: The Rosé Vignes de Nicole by Paul Mas is made from the typical Mediterranean grapes Grenache (40%), Cinsault (40%) and Syrah (20%). Stylistically a modern rosé with light color and a charming berry scent, the palate is characterized by elegant lightness and balanced mildness, the final is equally light and yet long lasting. Try it with summer salads or light grilled meats, seafood or just like that. A great rose and a price sensation.

Data.Name: Canadian Mist
Data.Description: Canadian Mist is a true blended whisky. It’s the world’s first whisky that uses fresh water from Georgian Bay, one of North America’s freshest water sources. Made at Canada’s oldest continuously owned and operated distillery in Collingwood, Ontario, Canadian Mist is aged in the finest white oak barrels, and charred to exact specifications to impart its smooth vanilla flavor. A soft, light sweetness dissolves into a mild oak profile.

Data.Name: Moskato Life Rosé
Data.Description: Embracing the extraordinary moments of life and celebrating achievable luxury, the Moskato Life salutes those who are celebrating life to the fullest, day in and day out. It’s an opportunity to experience opulence without added sacrifice and the perfect way to make any occasion toast worthy. With its flawless combination of light carbonation and sweetness, it drinks smooth and sparkles as bright as the toast makers themselves.

Data.Name: Josh Cellars Rosé
Data.Description:
Crisp, refreshing and bright: our Rosé is perfect for sunsets and warm summer days. This wine is light and easy-to-drink with flavors of white peach and strawberry and hints of nectarine.

“Rosé was one of the first wines I ever tried. Our Rosé takes me back to memories of carefree warm, summer days with family and good friends.” 

– Joseph Carr

Data.Name: Huber Hugo Sparkling Rose
Data.Description: 10th generation winegrower Markus Huber manages this 200+ year-old family operation, and it is under his expert leadership that Huber Hugo has gained international recognition as the star of Austria's Traisental region. His "Hugo" family of wines represent excellent values for everyday drinking. Made from a blend of Zweigelt and Pinot Noir from small single vineyards in the Traisental, this delicate and fresh sparkling rose offers juicy berry fruit and spice aromas and flavors with hints of mineral and citrus.

Data.Name: Girl Go Lightly Rosé
Data.Description: There’s a pleasantly light, silky texture on this pretty rose-gold colored blend. It has rich flavors of red cherries, persimmons and spices. One thing to know is that it’s quite sweet, like sugared tea.

Data.Name: Feudi Di San Gregorio Ros'aura Rosé
Data.Description: Blended from pure Aglianico grapes from the well maintained vineyards makes the Beneventano Rosato IGT Ros'aura rose wine to have an international recognition. Refreshing red fruity feel on the palate.

Data.Name: Culitos Moscato Rosé
Data.Description: Sweet and juicy flavors of peach, apricot and vanilla. Enjoy chilled with your favorite foods and friends.

Data.Name: Chloe Rosé
Data.Description: Extraordinary grapes from prized vineyards in California's Central Coast define the elegant style of this dry Rose. Delicate flavors and aromas of fresh strawberries, raspberries and watermelon unfold into a crisp, well-balanced wine.

Data.Name: Cloud Chaser Côtes de Provence Rosé
Data.Description:
In the glass, Cloud Chaser is a beautiful classic light pink Rosé color. The wine has an intense nose of tropical fruits, including mango and banana. Round and smooth in the mouth, Cloud Chaser has a lovely, complex onset and aromas of peach and apricot. The finish is long and lingering, yet the wine remains refreshing and quaffable. 

Cloud Chaser pairs perfectly with fish, Asian and Mediterranean cuisines, grilled and roasted meats, and pasta.

Data.Name: Champagne Eclipsia Extra Brut
Data.Description: Quite complex nose. Lively, and fresh with zesty citrus fruit, green apple, stone fruit, mineral flavours, and slight brioche notes.

Data.Name: Champagne Eclipsia Rosé
Data.Description:
Nose: Raspberry, cherry, floral, cake. 

Palate: Smooth, silky texture, nice finish and length! 

Grape Varieties: 80% Pinot Noir, 20% Chardonnay fermented in oak barrels for 37%.

Data.Name: Endless Crush Rosé
Data.Description: A lovely, harmonious rose, with everything balanced and nothing out of place. Utterly dry and quite elegant, with a pinkish onion-skin color and an acidity that guides the fruit through the long finish.

Data.Name: Dona Maria Rosé
Data.Description: Fresh and tropical fruit sensations. Very fresh and fruity. Pleasant sense of tropical fruits and strawberry. Very good acidity and persistent finish.

Data.Name: Chateau Minuty Cotes de Provence Rosé
Data.Description:
A magnificent wine of pleasure : the aromatic harmony of grenache and cinsault offers some notes of peach and candied orange. the mouth is fresh and round.
 
Origin: The grapes are carefully selected and come from the best soils of Cotes de Provence and come from vines cultivated in integrated farm way. 

Grapes varieties used : Grenache, Cinsault, Syrah

Data.Name: Charles & Charles Rose
Data.Description: "This wine is a pretty, pale-salmon color. Aromas of strawberry bubblegum, herb, tropical fruit and citrus peel lead to dry fruit flavors, full of papaya, guava and pink-grapefruit notes with a tart finish. It flat-out delivers."

Data.Name: Rodney Strong Rosé
Data.Description: This fine new offering is whimsically packaged with a screw cap and a floral label. That spirit is further evidenced by the wine's pretty pink color and subdued, light building of flavor, highlighted by orange, peach and strawberry notes and a substantial bite of mouthwatering acidity.

Data.Name: Domaine Chandon Rosé
Data.Description: In the glass, our Rosé is a pretty pink with intense ripe strawberry, juicy watermelon, and fresh red cherry fruit aromas and flavors. On the palate, this wine is creamy and seductive with a defined structure from the Pinot Noir added in its final stages.

Data.Name: Rosatello Rosé
Data.Description: This delectably sweet blush wine is easy to love with its tempting aromas of pomegranates and red currants. Taste the luscious flavor of fresh-picked strawberries and ripe cherries. Serve chilled.

Data.Name: The Dreaming Tree Rosé
Data.Description:
"Our Rose is good for everybody earlier in the day, and just fine for anybody in the middle of the day, and most everybody can enjoy it in the evening." - Dave Matthews

Food Pairing Notes:
A great sipping wine that pairs well with grilled chicken salad, bruschetta, asparagus salad, and mixed berry fruit tarts.


Tasting Notes:
This dry California Rosé is a soft light pink in color with delicate floral and tropical aromas. Crisp and light in body with fresh, fruity flavors of watermelon, strawberry, and nectarine.

Data.Name: Maine Beer Company Zoe
Data.Description: Tastes of pine and raisin predominate with notes of citrus and ripe dark berries. Malty backbone of toasted bread, dark chocolate and caramel. ABV 7.2%.

Data.Name: Maine Beer Company Another One
Data.Description: Tastes of pineapple, mango, and guava, with notes of orange and grapefruit. Undertones of earthy, woody pine. ABV 7%.

Data.Name: Maine Beer Company Mean Old Tom
Data.Description: Tastes of vanilla, coffee and roasted cereal with dark chocolate and a silky mouthfeel. ABV 6.5%.

Data.Name: Maine Beer Company Peeper Pale Ale
Data.Description: Taste of lemon, grapefruit and fresh cut grass. Delicate notes of raspberry, strawberry, pine, floral and faint bread. ABV 5.5%.

Data.Name: Maine Beer Company Lunch IPA
Data.Description: Lunch is a special whale that has been spotted off the Maine coast since 1982. She has what looks like a bite taken out of her fin, which adds to her unique character. This beer is dedicated to her determination and persistence. Keep on swimming! Tastes of orange, grapefruit, and lemon. With pine, and herbal undertones, tropical notes of guava and papaya with subtle caramel and malt sweetness. ABV 7%.

Data.Name: Maine Beer Company A Tiny Beautiful Something
Data.Description: Tastes of orange marmalade and apricot with floral perfume notes, spicy and earthy. ABV 5.5%.

Data.Name: Maine Beer Company Post Ride Snack
Data.Description: Who knows why biking and beer go together so well, but they just do. Maine Beer Company brewed this session IPA as a refreshing post ride snack with notes and aromas of tropical fruits, citrus, mixed berries, and grassy pine. Cheers to every ride! ABV 4.9%.

Data.Name: Tecate Original
Data.Description: A well balanced bright golden lager beer with a malt crisp flavor, low to medium bitterness that finishes clean. 4.5% ABV.

Data.Name: Stone Tropic of Thunder Lager
Data.Description: This beer showcases love for, and experimentation with hops using Mosaic, Citra, and newcomer Cashmere. These three combine to form an array of citrus, tropical and fruit aromas and flavors in a refreshing, crushable lager. Tastes of ripe Cantaloupe, citrus and passion fruit. Flavors of fresh hops with white wine and biscuit. 5.8% ABV.

Data.Name: Sol Cerveza Especial
Data.Description: A bright and refreshing Mexican lager with a smooth taste and a crisp finish. 4.5% ABV.

Data.Name: Mike's Hard Watermelon
Data.Description:
This "one in a melon" lemonade is gluten-removed and actually tastes like a true watermelon...with less seeds. Enjoy this refreshing summer treat.

ABV: 5%

Data.Name: Michelob Ultra Lime and Prickly Pear Cactus
Data.Description: Meet Michelob ULTRA Infusions Lime and Prickly Pear Cactus. A superior light beer infused with lime peels and prickly pear cactus, loaded with exotic taste and free of artificial colors and flavors. It’s beer meets exotic fruit, at only 95 calories per bottle.

Data.Name: Lagunitas Daytime IPA
Data.Description: The beer in this can has achieved what we all hope for ourselves; to be made new again. There is freedom in burning down the house of expectations and it confers an undeniable lightness to being. At 4% ABV and only 98 calories, DayTime IPA represents everything about making hop-forward beer, expressed in a sotto voice.

Data.Name: Dogfish Head Dragons and YumYums
Data.Description: An explosion of fruit in every sip, Dragons & YumYums is an intensely tropical - yet subtlety bitter - pale ale brewed with a combination of dragon fruit, yumberry, passionfruit, pear juice and black carrot juice. Clocking in at 6.5% ABV and 25 IBU, Dragons & YumYums is a first-of-its-kind collaboration with American rock icons, The Flaming Lips.

Data.Name: Goose Island Summertime
Data.Description:
With a light fruity aroma and a bright, crisp finish, Goose Island Summertime Kölsch is the perfect summer session ale.  A Kölsch beer brewed in the traditional German fashion, you’ll find yourself enjoying and savoring each sip of Summertime as much as you do those hot summer days and cool summer nights.

ABV: 5%

Data.Name: Goose Island County Brand Stout
Data.Description:
A liquid as dark and dense as a black hole with thick foam the color of a bourbon barrel. The nose is an intense mix of charred oak, chocolate, vanilla, caramel and smoke. One sip has more flavor than your average case of beer.

ABV: 14.7%

Data.Name: Avery Brewing Co White Rascal
Data.Description:
An authentic Belgian style white ale, this Rascal is unfiltered and cleverly spiced with coriander and Curaçao orange peel producing a refreshingly zesty classic ale.

5.6% ABV.

Data.Name: Avery Brewing Liliko'i Kepolo Begian Ale
Data.Description:
Adding a tropical island flair to a spicy traditional witbier, Liliko'i Kepolo erupts with monumental passionfruit aroma and acidity along with a sublimely succulent finish.

5.4% ABV.

Data.Name: Bud Light Orange
Data.Description: Bud Light Orange is back! Brewed with real orange peels for a new way to taste summer refreshment.  The clean, crisp and refreshing taste you love with a hint of orange flavor in every sip.  Enjoy it today, and anytime the summer mood strikes!

Data.Name: Beck's
Data.Description: Beck's is renowned for uncompromising quality. It is brewed today, as it was in 1873, with a rigorous brewing process and a recipe using only the best 100% natural ingredients - hops, water, barley and malt. Beck's adheres to the strictest quality standards, consistent with the German Reinheitsgebot (Purity Law), and enjoys wide popularity in almost 90 countries.

Data.Name: Angry Orchard Green Apple Cider
Data.Description: A gorgeous amber cider with bright, fresh apple aromas and notes of honey dew melon and kiwi. A pleasantly tart blend of lively apple flavor and balanced sweetness. Enjoy!

Data.Name: Cambridge Brewing Working Class Hero
Data.Description: American grisette-style saison with orange and lemon peel, coriander, and Citra hops.

Data.Name: Cambridge Brewing Flower Child
Data.Description: Extensively hopped and dryhopped with a big roster of hops – Simcoe, Centennial, Cascade, Ahtanum, Chinook, and Amarillo – it’s big, bright, and floral, with just enough malt to balance. This American-style I.P.A. stands head and shoulders above its hoppy brethren, blending pale and honey malts to balance the palate without interfering in your herbal reverie, and creating a new American classic. – Cambridge Brewing Company.

Data.Name: Cambridge Brewing Remain In Light
Data.Description: A hint of wood mingles with the minerally bite of carbonation from afar. Up close: spicy wood, hints of resin, dried tarragon and some sweet notes in the background—like wayward strands of cotton candy. Graham cracker malt notes when warmer. Quite woodsy. Very light sulfur note. Overall: a lovely beer! Bitterness is in line with expectations for pils—pronounced but not overly assertive. Classic Europe an hops. Complex.

Data.Name: Bud Light Lime
Data.Description: Bud Light Lime is brewed using a combination of barley malts, non-malted cereal grains, subtle hopping and natural lime flavor.

Data.Name: Fishers Island Lemonade
Data.Description: Fishers Island Lemonade is a craft cocktail containing premium vodka and whiskey spirits, natural lemon and honey flavor at 9% ABV. Fishers Island Lemonade is the house recipe from a family bar located on Fishers Island, NY.

Data.Name: Coors Banquet Beer
Data.Description: The Banquet Beer was born in the Rockies and has been a proud part of the American experience for generations, stubbornly refusing to compromise, since 1873.

Data.Name: Clausthaler Amber Non-Alcoholic
Data.Description: Pours a light honey/orange color. Aromas of sweet bready malts, grassy hops, honey, and tea leaves. Tastes of sweet bread, caramel, and grain with a grassy, hoppy finish. Reminiscent of southern sweet tea.

Data.Name: Cisco Sankaty Light
Data.Description: A light American Golden Lager. This delicious creation is light-bodied with tremendous balance and distinct hop character. At 3.8% alcohol and 126 calories this light beer has true flavor and body while being easy to drink and easier on the waistline. It is named after the famous lighthouse that has stood on a bluff on the southeastern side of Nantucket Island since 1849. Size: 12 oz ABV 3.8%

Data.Name: Hopsters IPA
Data.Description:
Founders Range India Pale Ale The second members’ competition-winning beer brings us a classic American style India Pale Ale. This beer is all about the hops: pine and uplifted citrus characteristics sustain the pleasant lingering bitterness, that is balanced by the mild malt body. This beer is for the serious beer lover.

6.5% ABV

Data.Name: Hopsters Comet Mosaic IPA
Data.Description: This beer from Hopsters has a smell of grass, lemon, and fresh strawberries. The taste is a delicious minty citrus,

Data.Name: Hopsters Comet Citra IPA
Data.Description: A balanced New England IPA that effortlessly blends the tart bitterness of Comet hops with the juicy, tropical aromas of Citra hops. Together with Two-Row and White Wheat malts, this beer provides an upfront splash of bright grapefruit and luscious undertones of tropical mango and papaya fruits.

Data.Name: Johnnie Walker Double Black
Data.Description: Hand selected whiskies defined by hints of smoldering charcoal, and burnt timber matured in deep-charred oak casks. A smoky intense experience with a smoky nose, unmistakable spice and slight notes of dark fruit followed by a lingering smoky finish. Enjoy neat.

Data.Name: Bon & Viv Spiked Seltzer Grapefruit
